NAME

AnyEvent::UserAgent - AnyEvent::HTTP OO-wrapper.

DESCRIPTION

AnyEvent::UserAgent is a OO-wrapper around AnyEvent::HTTP with cookies
support by HTTP::Cookies. Also request callback receives response as
HTTP::Response object.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc
command.

    perldoc AnyEvent::UserAgent

You can also look for information at:

    Repository
        http://github.com/AdCampRu/anyevent-useragent
    Bug tracker
        http://github.com/AdCampRu/anyevent-useragent/issues

